                <p>My service, a survey site, uses machine learning to predict how factors like bullying, parenting, and home environment may impact a child's future. By identifying these issues and offering solutions, we aim to support children in reaching their full potential and fostering healthier adulthood outcomes.</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <script src="scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
